perty we call uniform regularity of tails. Finally,\nwe prove that every graphon is equivalent to a graphon on $\\mathbb{R}_+$\nequipped with Lebesgue measure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2016 19:10:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 20 Aug 2016 07:42:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 18 Aug 2017 16:28:04 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 20 Jun 2018 14:12:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-21"}
