ll and subsonic. Most starless cores in\nPerseus are either not in a state of collapse or expansion, or are in a very\nearly stage of collapse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2016 20:55:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
