equality $C_T^{\\textrm{UV}} >\nC_T^{\\textrm{IR}}$ applies both to the GN and the scalar $O(N)$ models in\n$d=3$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2016 21:47:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Feb 2016 20:21:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-12"}
