s that invoke beaming in\nthat frame at much lower energies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jan 2016 13:01:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Feb 2016 12:10:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 3 Jul 2016 12:09:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-17"}
